# Java to Kotlin Tool

Intellij/Android Studio has a handy tool for Java developers: Java to Kotlin converter. 

This tool makes it easy to convert java code to kotlin code.

To become familiar with it, please copy the following class (Java) and paste in to the test file.

```
public class Person {
    private final String name;
    private final int age;

    public Person(String name, int age) {
        this.name = name;
        this.age = age;
    }

    public String getName() {
        return name;
    }

    public int getAge() {
        return age;
    }
}
```

